description: Restaurant apportez votre vin servant une cuisine du marché Additional Information Le Bistro le coup monté est le tout nouveau restaurant branché « apportez votre vin » de Repentigny. ... Situé en plein centre-ville, le Bistro le coup monté se veut une réponse à une demande pressante dans la région: une table haut de gamme où l’on peut apporter ses meilleures bouteilles de vin. Au Bistro le coup monté, vous retrouverez une cuisine d’inspiration française faisant la part belle aux produits locaux. Le menu du chef Benjamin De Châteauneuf est composé de classiques de la cuisine bistro traditionnelle ainsi que de plats inspirés par ses 10 années d’expérience dans plusieurs restaurants renommés de Montréal. Raffinée et sans prétention, la cuisine du bistro est toujours savoureuse et respectueuse des producteurs locaux. Bien ancré dans son époque, le menu tient compte des saisons et des arrivages. Le Bistro le coup monté est issu de la collaboration entre le chef copropriétaire Benjamin de Châteauneuf, Matthieu Bonneau, Betty-Anne Plante et Simon Fichault.

description: We help families go through divorce with dignity and respect and make sure that the children were suffering as little as possible in this process. Additional Information We have 4 Offices to Serve You Better : Alt Divorce Embrun 964 Notre-Dame... P.O. Box 749 Embrun, Ontario K0A 1W0 Alt Divorce Embrun Ottawa Centre World Exchange Plaza 45 O’Connor Street, Suite 1150 Ottawa, Ontario K1P 1A4 What is the ALT Divorce Way? ALT Divorce is a new way to separate without having to go to court. It is a process where a team of professionals, not just lawyers, take care of ALL the members of a family to help them move forward and settle all their matters, legal and non-legal, in a cost and time effective manner. The ALT Divorce Way was created to help families go through divorce with dignity and respect and make sure that the children were suffering as little as possible in this process. What are the benefits if I choose the ALT Divorce Way? First, we’re more than just lawyers. At ALT Divorce, our family consultants are at the heart of our process. He/she will support you and your spouse throughout this journey, guide you through the emotional stages of your separation and assist you to resolve all of the non-legal disputes that may arise from time to time between you and your ex-spouse. That way, you are not paying for legal expertise when the matters that you need resolved do not require legal expertise. Secondly, doing it the ALT Divorce Way will, without a doubt, cost you less than going to court or to fight it out between lawyers. Nowadays, it costs at least $3,000 just to start a divorce action. Every other step in the court process (and there are many) will cost you an average of $5,000, and there is simply no way your lawyer can tell you how much it will ultimately cost. If you chose the ALT Divorce Way, you will have a much better idea of how much your separation is going to cost you, and we guarantee it will be a whole lot less than court. The third benefit is that your separation will be resolved much quicker. When all of the needs of each member of the family are being taken care of by the right professional, under one roof, it can take as little as a few months, sometimes weeks, to resolve everything. Even when the needs of your family are significant, or when the legal matters are complex, they will be resolved much faster when the right professional is working with both spouses to help them reach a common goal. Finally, when you use the ALT Divorce Way, YOU are in control. If you go to court, the judge does not take your feelings into consideration when making a decision, nor does he or she consider whether there would be alternative options that would address everybody’s needs better. The judge’s job is to impose a decision based on the law, period, and you have no control over the outcome. If you do it the ALT Divorce Way, our professionals will help your family craft a settlement that meets everybody’s needs, including those of your children. What can I expect from ALT Divorce? The story follows Troy Carrington as he tries to save his local footy club, the Roosters. Special tickets are available for community groups & sports clubs, starting from $12. Call Sue Brown on (03) 535...5 0292 for more info. Tickets are also available at the door or via Ararat Town Hall's website. Since 1998, CIMT College has been guiding and training both local and international students by providing them learning experiences that meet international standards and benchmarks. The college provides an opportunity for professional growth and development across the areas of technology, healthcare, business and management. CIMT College is located in Greater Toronto Area and has four campuses – Malton Campus, Mississauga Campus, Brampton Campus and Scarborough Campus. All locations are in close proximity with the International Airport and easy access through air, bus and rail. CIMT College helps every student in choosing the right career path through its rigorously monitored admission and placement process. From the admission to the placements, the students are placed on a continuum of learning that develops them as thorough professionals. Students join us with their personal aspirations and we strive to help the students fulfill their aspirations by providing them an environment of collaborative effort, experienced faculty and supportive staff. The faculty at CIMT College is well versed with the theoretical as well as practical aspect of the courses to train the students on finer skills for their professional success. The college offers a variety of job oriented and career focused diploma and post graduate diploma programs that allow students to enter into their choice of profession with a strong knowledge and expertise of the field. Since its inception, CIMT College has been providing programs that offer an apt combination of theory and practice. In today’s world, to sustain in the workforce and to be continually productive in the job, you need to constantly upgrade your knowledge and skills. CIMT College offers you an opportunity to train in and explore new areas of professional skills and knowledge. We offer a variety of short courses for ongoing skill enhancement education and retraining along with the professional courses necessary for registration with various regulated professions in the field of technology, healthcare, business and management. Every program is developed in consultation with the relevant industry standards to achieve the highest academic and professional standards. We at CIMT College are committed to academic offerings relevant to industry practices for better employment avenues hence placement services offered to our graduates adds a significant value to the students’ employability. We aim at offering our students with a heightened intellectual and cultural sensitivity through professional, ethical and technological expertise in their chosen profession. CIMT College is a Cisco Networking Academy, Microsoft IT Academy, Microsoft IT Academy and certified training partner with CompTIA, thus providing unmatched and unparalleled quality education to its students. CIMT College houses an authorized in-house online testing centre powered by PearsonVUE and Prometric. Our Vision: CIMT College is a centre of academic and professional excellence that nurtures the students to ensure their all round education and development so as to make them a valuable asset in the global society. Our Mission: CIMT College aims at transforming the lives of all those who enter the portals of CIMT College by providing them with education and training for success.
